{"tid":2214248,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"父親因買錯PS5被15歲兒子毆打","createTime":"2020-09-23T06:04:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-23T08:56:18.000Z","uid":26018,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"78a2b30d0bc28215944e9dbec21f1270e8946b91","tid":2214248,"uid":26018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T06:04:57.000Z","msg":"日本警視廳於12日以傷害罪嫌疑，在東京都中野區，逮捕了一名以類似鈍器的物體毆打父親的的少年（15歲）。由於母親看到兒子的暴行而馬上加以阻止，父親只受了輕傷。<br />\n根據調查，少年和父親（42歲）約好，要父親替他購買於11月12日發售的攜帶遊戲機PS5。不過從早上就去排隊的父親，卻買回了一款型號為 PS5HMSD 的碎紙機，這讓少年相當惱火。在吃早飯時，少年拿起放在餐桌上的水果刀旁邊的法式麵包（長30釐米），不斷毆打父親。<br />\n<br />\n聽到父親的慘叫的母親急忙來阻止了少年，不過父親的額頭還是受了輕微的毆傷。少年被附近接到報告的警察逮捕。在調查中少年供訴到：「一想到他那麼早出去到底去排了什麼隊，就惱火的不得了。」<br />\n<br />\n警視廳表示，今後類似這種由於親子間對遊戲的理解溝通不充分，而引發的暴力事件，還將有可能發生，請大家引以為戒。<br />\n日本生活用品牌子 Iris ohyama 在 2013 年推出一款型號為 PS5HMSD 的碎紙機，除了與 PS5「撞名」，其外型亦與 PS5 一樣，以黑白色作機身主要顏色，咋看確是有點相似，令官方也在其 Twitter 上發佈帖文，勸大家不要買錯，更開玩笑指如果買錯的話，不但無法玩遊戲，還會碎掉遊戲光碟。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tx8UxhB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTx8UxhB.jpg&h=f9bf4d6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://eoeonews.com/doc_dXNNa3phbDNKVXh5UnpFYTI3ZHVRdz09?fbclid=IwAR0HcIS-Va4_HGKQTytQ4zw5X3hShc44Ufm2ZmT_ptXEoTkWQuxvR6gqaDc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Feoeonews.com%2Fdoc_dXNNa3phbDNKVXh5UnpFYTI3ZHVRdz09%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0HcIS-Va4_HGKQTytQ4zw5X3hShc44Ufm2ZmT_ptXEoTkWQuxvR6gqaDc&d=UZIDdMkqB5nEVwovtN1d9vcKxKGkGiqypQ%2FDN8PQntA%3D&h=203808ff\" target=\"_blank\">http://eoeonews.com/doc_dXNNa3phbDNKVXh5UnpFYTI3ZHVRdz09?fbclid=IwAR0HcIS-Va4_HGKQTytQ4zw5X3hShc44Ufm2ZmT_ptXEoTkWQuxvR6gqaDc</a><br />\n<br />\n咁癲個仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />應該會打到內傷！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"192c8f13084a1ca6b7138998f44dfb01f35d53fd","tid":2214248,"uid":58253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T06:16:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />老竇真係慘"},{"pid":"bec4a41e3a674cb67efb5b6400841b654844a629","tid":2214248,"uid":31323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T06:38:44.000Z","msg":"咁就過咗16年"},{"pid":"22ea2bafd3b3d67bd3411b31fc9358e4c795b7aa","tid":2214248,"uid":4709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T08:53:56.000Z","msg":"父親因買錯PS5被毆打<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2212851\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2212851</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"55f9d77ca5e8503d5fc1ec22dd3dffa3eca8c9a1","tid":2214248,"uid":292497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T08:55:49.000Z","msg":"囉法包打老豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />篇文幾多年"},{"pid":"a39fe58c74d3cec010712e98a950b4731d9b77d9","tid":2214248,"uid":261873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T08:56:18.000Z","msg":"型過ps5<br />\n又實用"}]}